. 
.         ********************* Targeting-relevant indicators ******************
. 
. *   Duration of stay in Turkiye
. **  In continuous years: 
.         sum time_in_turkey

{txt}    Variable {c |}        Obs        Mean    Std. dev.       Min        Max
{hline 13}{c +}{hline 57}
time_in_tu~y {c |}{res}      2,001    9.687156    2.396055          1         16
{txt}
{com}. ** Cut-off points – one or less (new arrivals), 2-4 years, 5-8 years, 9+ years 
.         gen time_in_turkey_cat = cond(mi(time_in_turkey),  0,                   ///
>                                                          cond(time_in_turkey <= 1, 1,                   ///
>                                                          cond(time_in_turkey <= 5, 2,                   ///
>                                                          cond(time_in_turkey <= 8, 3, 4)))) 
{txt}
{com}. 
. *       Duration of stay in current camp
. **  In continuous years
.         sum time_in_thiscamp

