{hline 13}{c +}{hline 57}
time_in_th~p {c |}{res}      2,001    6.257871    3.994305          0         16
{txt}
{com}. **  Cut-off points – one or less (new arrivals), 2-4 years, 5-8 years, 9+ years
.         gen time_in_thiscamp_cat = cond(mi(time_in_thiscamp),  0,               ///
>                                                            cond(time_in_thiscamp <= 1, 1,               ///
>                                                            cond(time_in_thiscamp <= 5, 2,               ///
>                                                            cond(time_in_thiscamp <= 8, 3, 4)))) 
{txt}
